Decay B_s0sig
0.66   MyD'_s1-   mu+    nu_mu        PHOTOS  ISGW2;
0.33   MyD_s2*-   mu+    nu_mu        PHOTOS  ISGW2;

  #
Enddecay
CDecay anti-B_s0sig


Decay MyD'_s1-
